STATE of North Carolina
v.
Derrick D. BOGER No. 158P06-9 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 20, 2016 Derrick D. Boger, For Boger, Derrick D. Mary Carla Babb, Assistant Attorney General, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 20th of September 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cabarrus County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of September 2016."
